or he's gonna be damned!

838
00:57:57.545 --> 00:58:00.548
Marcus is damned.
Marcus is damned.

839
00:58:01.849 --> 00:58:03.250
If the curse is in the knife,

840
00:58:03.351 --> 00:58:04.585
